# skip-rule: trasno-file_reverse
#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifies <filename>Makefile</filename>(s) to add debug info"
msgstr ""
"Modifica os ficheiros <filename>Makefile</filename> para engadir información "
"de depuración."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>adddebug</command> <group><option>-k</option></group> "
"<group><option>-r</option></group> <group><option>-n</option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>adddebug</command> <group><option>-k</option></group> "
"<group><option>-r</option></group> <group><option>-n</option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descrición"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>adddebug</command> modifies the <filename>Makefile</filename> in "
"the current directory (and optionally in its subdirectories) to add debug "
"info (<option>-g3</option>). It will also remove optimisations (<option>-"
"O[1-9]</option>)."
msgstr ""
"<command>adddebug</command> modifica o <filename>Makefile</filename> no "
"cartafol actual (e opcionalmente nos subcartafoles) para engadirlle "
"información de depuración (<option>-g3</option>). Tamén retirará "
"optimizacións (<option>-O[1-9]</option>)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Esta utilidade forma parte do equipamento de desenvolvemento de programas de "
"&kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcións"

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-k</option>"
msgstr "<option>-k</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep optimisations (do not remove <option>-O[1-9]?</option> flags which are "
"removed by default)."
msgstr ""
"Mantén as optimizacións (non retira as marcas <option>-O[1-9]?</option> que "
"se retiran de maneira predeterminada)."

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-r</option>"
msgstr "<option>-r</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recursively search through all subdirectories of the current directory and "
"operate on every <filename>Makefile</filename> that is found."
msgstr ""
"Busca recursivamente en todos os subcartafoles do cartafol actual e opera en "
"cada <filename>Makefile</filename> que atope."

#. Tag: option
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>-n</option>"
msgstr "<option>-n</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-adddebug.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"compile without NDEBUG and NO_DEBUG being defined (makes <function>kDebug</"
"function> calls work)"
msgstr ""
"compila sen definir NDEBUG e NO_DEBUG (fai que as chamadas a "
"<function>kDebug</function> funcionen)"

